  <sect2>
    <title>Installation of libxcb</title>

    <para>
      Suppress installation of unnecessary files:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed "s/ install-data-local//" -i doc/Makefile.in</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Remove dependency on libpthread-stubs package which is useless on Linux:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed "s/pthread-stubs//" -i configure</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Prepare the package for compilation:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure $XORG_CONFIG \
            --enable-xinput</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Compile the package:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Install the package:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make -j1 install
rm -v /usr/lib/libxcb*.la</userinput></screen>

    <sect3>
      <title>Command Explanations</title>

      <para>
        <parameter>--enable-xinput</parameter>: This switch enables XCB Xinput
        extension.
      </para>

    </sect3>

  </sect2>

